name: Maracá Power
description: Maracá it's an  indigenous percussion instrument that is naturally used into ayahuasca rituals, The spiritual activation it's instantaneous, being capable of transport us in time,  getting close to our ancients. This is the 2/4 piece of the serie " Nature Ambience", put your headphones on and join the journey! - This was a genuine spiritual improvise recorded at 2020, in a psychedelic ritual made by me and my friend Caio.
